bio: Hello! I was born and raised in New Jersey in the New York Metropolitan area.I focused my studies in Finance and Accounting, as well as some programming. After graduating from Fairleigh Dickinson University, I worked primarily in Accounting for 6 years before joining Ennead in 2014. Outside of work, I enjoy traveling, jogging, yoga, fitbit challenges, hiking, films, art, museums, live music, and technology.
